IntroIDG.cn: IDG founded in 2015 is a visualization group in Zhejiang University, P.R. China. Our research aims to create novel information visualization, visual analytics, augmented/virtual reality, and human computer interaction technology to empower users to do analytical reasoning with big data in various settings, such as urban informatics, sports analytics, behavior analytics, and social media analytics.
